experiences:
Plenitude is an Energy Benefit Corporation (Benefit Company) , with an end-to-end approach to sustainability, from energy production to its responsible use. Core business: Renewables, Retail & Electric Vehicles Recharge. We operate in 13 countries, 2600 total employees .
Directly reporting to CEO, together with my team I oversee
- HR functions: Organization, Development & Training, People management & Administration, Compensation&Benefit, Union Relations; Labour Disputes, Labour Planning & Control, International Management;
- Sustainability & ESG: strategy definition, positioning and reporting of sustainability and ESG (Environmental, Social, Governance), identification and development of sustainability initiatives;
- Internal Communication , Change Management , Cultural Transformation; 
- Diversity & Inclusion;
- People Experience: defining innovative solutions for a better working experience 
- HSE: managing health, safety & environment process ("Datore di Lavoro ex D.lgs 81/2008)
- Security & Fraud Management

